  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/59d7ee232fa1c9cdc2a7fff38604038c.poster.avif?t=1734932612\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/59d7ee232fa1c9cdc2a7fff38604038c.webm?t=1734932612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/59d7ee232fa1c9cdc2a7fff38604038c.mp4?t=1734932612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Old Skool Racer is a complete arcade racing game world that recreates the sheer thrill of classic arcade racing games such as Outrun, Screamer, Star Wars Pod Racer and WaveRace 64. It features racing using cars, speedboats, hoverpods and chariots.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Core Game Features</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tChoose from four different vehicle types including cars, speedboats, hoverpods and chariots</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tOver 15 day and night locations such as New York, Venice, Flooded City, Borneo, Canada, Yosemite, Amsterdam, India, Africa, Norway, Switzerland, Egypt and Utopia</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tWin new vehicles by winning Championship races</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tSingleplayer game modes include Quick Race, Time Trial and Championship</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Four player multiplayer, achievements, and 3D trophies </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/788a7e491f1bff963fa88d2b692f9ba0.poster.avif?t=1734932612\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/788a7e491f1bff963fa88d2b692f9ba0.webm?t=1734932612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/788a7e491f1bff963fa88d2b692f9ba0.mp4?t=1734932612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Garage Customisation</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tCustomise your vehicle’s appearance using a combination of special parts, paint colours, decals, and materials</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tChoose the exact colour from millions of colours using a Photoshop-style colour pallette</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tSelect from multiple material types such as matte, fibreglass, glossy metal, gold, aluminium, and pearl </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tAdd decals to your vehicle from the included library or choose from your own personal collection </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tCustomise your car using parts such as spoilers and wheel rims</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/63c0b81684ed347c06be0993117479f1.poster.avif?t=1734932612\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/63c0b81684ed347c06be0993117479f1.webm?t=1734932612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/63c0b81684ed347c06be0993117479f1.mp4?t=1734932612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Winner’s Island</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tUnlock your own beautiful Winner's Island, a luxury mansion, and a toy train</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tDecorate your luxury mansion using furniture, carpets, paintings and chandeliers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tCompletely change the appearance of your mansion to suit your taste. Select from a collection of realistic wall paints, floor, and roof tile</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tWin Championship races and display the winning trophies in the 3D Trophy Room inside your mansion</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tWash your cars in your own private car wash</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/59d7ee232fa1c9cdc2a7fff38604038c.poster.avif?t=1734932612\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/59d7ee232fa1c9cdc2a7fff38604038c.webm?t=1734932612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/59d7ee232fa1c9cdc2a7fff38604038c.mp4?t=1734932612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Old Skool Racer is a complete arcade racing game world that recreates the sheer thrill of classic arcade racing games such as Outrun, Screamer, Star Wars Pod Racer and WaveRace 64. It features racing using cars, speedboats, hoverpods and chariots.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Core Game Features</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tChoose from four different vehicle types including cars, speedboats, hoverpods and chariots</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tOver 15 day and night locations such as New York, Venice, Flooded City, Borneo, Canada, Yosemite, Amsterdam, India, Africa, Norway, Switzerland, Egypt and Utopia</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tWin new vehicles by winning Championship races</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tSingleplayer game modes include Quick Race, Time Trial and Championship</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Four player multiplayer, achievements, and 3D trophies </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/788a7e491f1bff963fa88d2b692f9ba0.poster.avif?t=1734932612\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285310/extras/788a7e491f1bff963fa88d2b